The paper also involves graphics tasks related to rendering and generative models, which suggest cs.GR (Computer Graphics) as the second likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves deep learning techniques, which suggest cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as likely sub-categories.
